data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Kern subdivision! This remodeled modern 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is designed to impress. Step inside and be amazed by the open-style concept, with the kitchen seamlessly flowing into the spacious living and dining room area. Prepare to fall in love with the kitchen as it is equipped with granite countertops, a kitchen island, and trendy shaker cabinets. The large backyard sliding doors bring in an abundance of natural sunlight, creating a warm and inviting ambiance in the dining area. The master bedroom has a sliding barndoor that leads into an en-suite bathroom, providing privacy and a touch of rustic charm. With ample space throughout, this house offers endless possibilities for you and your family. Whether you're looking for room to grow or spaces to entertain guests, this home has it all. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own your own slice of paradise in the Kern subdivision. Make this house yours today!
